<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .header-image {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            background-position: center;
        }
        .center {
            display: block;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            width: 50%;

        }
        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            width: 100%;
        }
        th, td {
            border: 1px solid black;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<img src="cid:ong-manager-image" class="center" >

<h1>Notification: New User Interested in Joining</h1>
<p>Dear President ${firstNamePresident},</p>
<p>We hope this email finds you well. We are excited to inform you that a new user has expressed interest in joining the organization</p>
<p>Please take a moment to reach out to the user and discuss their interest in joining. You can contact them at the provided email address. </p>
<p>We believe their skills and enthusiasm could make a valuable contribution to our organization.</p>
<p>Thank you for your attention to this matter.</p>

<p>Best regards,</p>
<p>The ${organizationName} Team</p>


<table>
    <thead>
    <tr>
        <th>Contact Last Name</th>
        <th>Contact First Name</th>
        <th>Contact Email</th>
    </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
    <tr>
        <td>${lastNameUser}</td>
        <td>${firstNameUser}</td>
        <td>${emailUser}</td>
    </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>
</body>
</html>